                            <img src="~/images/Venice570x370.jpg" alt="" width="570" height="380" />
                        </figure>
                        <div class="caption">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </a>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="titled-gallery-caption text-center">Italy, Venice</div>
                    <p class="card-text font-weight-bold">There’s something extremely romantic and charming about Venice. Imagine strolling down alleyways, eating authentic gelato while window shopping for Italian leather handbags. Whether it’s the Basilica di San Marco located in the heart of the Piazza San Marco, the Rialto Bridge, or the Ponte dei Sospiri, there is so much history to be seen on this magical little island, it can seem very overwhelming.</p>
                    <br />
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">BUY IT!</a>
